  ('dietitian-moex-07384', 'dietitian', 'dietitian-moex-102-2755cf97', 'sub-dietitian-05', NULL, 'single_choice', '為避免增加心血管的負擔，脂肪對於長期照護的老年人而言是需要限制的營養素，一般建議脂肪攝取占 總熱量的：', '["15％～20％", "20％～25％", "25％～30％", "30％～35％"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:11:46+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "1f046f45edfe", "answer_pdf_sha1": "321124405641", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "102110", "c": "106", "s": "0303", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "膳食療養學", "year": "102", "exam_name": "102年第二次專技醫師中醫師分試中醫師營養師心理師護理師社會工作師、特考聽力牙體技術人員、法醫師語言聽力牙體技術師考試", "original_question_number": 40, "answer_corrected": true, "flags": ["answer_corrected_skip_v1"], "slug": "dietitian", "db_exam_id": "dietitian"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('dietitian-moex-07385', 'dietitian', 'dietitian-moex-102-da9d23a3', 'sub-dietitian-06', NULL, 'single_choice', '依據「食品衛生管理法」第39條規定，食品業者對於檢驗結果有異議者，得於收到有關通知後多少日內， 向原抽驗機關申請複驗？', '["3", "7", "10", "15"]'::jsonb, 3, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:11:47+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "c383b1a56582", "answer_pdf_sha1": "75330ea383a5", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "102110", "c": "106", "s": "0306", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "食品衛生與安全", "year": "102", "exam_name": "102年第二次專技醫師中醫師分試中醫師營養師心理師護理師社會工作師、特考聽力牙體技術人員、法醫師語言聽力牙體技術師考試", "original_question_number": 1, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "dietitian", "db_exam_id": "dietitian"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('dietitian-moex-07386', 'dietitian', 'dietitian-moex-102-da9d23a3', 'sub-dietitian-06', NULL, 'single_choice', '「食品業者良好衛生規範」一般規定，下列何者錯誤？', '["蓄水池每年至少清理1次", "蓄水池其設置地點應距化糞池3公尺以上", "使用地下水源者，其水源應與污染源至少保持5公尺之距離", "食品作業場所照明設施光線應達到100米燭光以上"]'::jsonb, 2, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:11:47+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "c383b1a56582", "answer_pdf_sha1": "75330ea383a5", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "102110", "c": "106", "s": "0306", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "食品衛生與安全", "year": "102", "exam_name": "102年第二次專技醫師中醫師分試中醫師營養師心理師護理師社會工作師、特考聽力牙體技術人員、法醫師語言聽力牙體技術師考試", "original_question_number": 2, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "dietitian", "db_exam_id": "dietitian"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('dietitian-moex-07387', 'dietitian', 'dietitian-moex-102-da9d23a3', 'sub-dietitian-06', NULL, 'single_choice', '依據「食品製造業者良好衛生規範」規定，庫存管理的原則是：', '["先進後出", "先進先出", "後進先出", "依原料種類而定"]'::jsonb, 1, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:11:47+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "c383b1a56582", "answer_pdf_sha1": "75330ea383a5", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "102110", "c": "106", "s": "0306", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "食品衛生與安全", "year": "102", "exam_name": "102年第二次專技醫師中醫師分試中醫師營養師心理師護理師社會工作師、特考聽力牙體技術人員、法醫師語言聽力牙體技術師考試", "original_question_number": 3, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "dietitian", "db_exam_id": "dietitian"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('dietitian-moex-07388', 'dietitian', 'dietitian-moex-102-da9d23a3', 'sub-dietitian-06', NULL, 'single_choice', '依據「食品販賣業者良好衛生規範」規定，冷藏食品之中心溫度應保持在多少℃以下凍結點以上？', '["12", "9", "7", "5"]'::jsonb, 2, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:11:47+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "c383b1a56582", "answer_pdf_sha1": "75330ea383a5", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "102110", "c": "106", "s": "0306", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "食品衛生與安全", "year": "102", "exam_name": "102年第二次專技醫師中醫師分試中醫師營養師心理師護理師社會工作師、特考聽力牙體技術人員、法醫師語言聽力牙體技術師考試", "original_question_number": 4, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "dietitian", "db_exam_id": "dietitian"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('dietitian-moex-07389', 'dietitian', 'dietitian-moex-102-da9d23a3', 'sub-dietitian-06', NULL, 'single_choice', '下列何種冷凍雞隻的解凍處理方式不恰當？', '["於4℃或以下冷藏室解凍後立即烹煮", "於微波爐中部分解凍後立即烹煮", "直接浸泡在冷水中後立即烹煮", "先放置在不透水包裝袋中，再於水溫21℃以下，以流水解凍後立即烹煮"]'::jsonb, 2, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:11:47+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "c383b1a56582", "answer_pdf_sha1": "75330ea383a5", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "102110", "c": "106", "s": "0306", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "食品衛生與安全", "year": "102", "exam_name": "102年第二次專技醫師中醫師分試中醫師營養師心理師護理師社會工作師、特考聽力牙體技術人員、法醫師語言聽力牙體技術師考試", "original_question_number": 5, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "dietitian", "db_exam_id": "dietitian"}'::jsonb, NULL),
