  ('dietitian-moex-07391', 'dietitian', 'dietitian-moex-102-da9d23a3', 'sub-dietitian-06', NULL, 'single_choice', '食品中存在的各種微生物間都會有某些相關性，不同種類的細菌、酵母菌、黴菌在食品中產生競爭，依 據食品所提供的特定環境與條件，產生微生物族群的消長，此種作用稱為：', '["共生作用（Symbiosis）", "相乘作用（Synergism）", "拮抗作用（Antagonism）", "發酵作用（Fermentation）"]'::jsonb, 2, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:11:47+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "c383b1a56582", "answer_pdf_sha1": "75330ea383a5", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "102110", "c": "106", "s": "0306", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "食品衛生與安全", "year": "102", "exam_name": "102年第二次專技醫師中醫師分試中醫師營養師心理師護理師社會工作師、特考聽力牙體技術人員、法醫師語言聽力牙體技術師考試", "original_question_number": 7, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "dietitian", "db_exam_id": "dietitian"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('dietitian-moex-07392', 'dietitian', 'dietitian-moex-102-da9d23a3', 'sub-dietitian-06', NULL, 'single_choice', '油炸洋芋片打開經過一段時間後，風味發生劣變，此過程稱為：', '["油脂氧化作用", "發酵", "糖解作用", "蛋白質水解"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:11:47+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "c383b1a56582", "answer_pdf_sha1": "75330ea383a5", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "102110", "c": "106", "s": "0306", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "食品衛生與安全", "year": "102", "exam_name": "102年第二次專技醫師中醫師分試中醫師營養師心理師護理師社會工作師、特考聽力牙體技術人員、法醫師語言聽力牙體技術師考試", "original_question_number": 8, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "dietitian", "db_exam_id": "dietitian"}'::jsonb, NULL),
